description: ABV Consulting, Inc. does not have significant operations. It focuses on acquiring target companies with operations located primarily in Southeast Asia, the Pacific Islands, Taiwan, and the People's Republic of China. Previously, the company provided consulting services. ABV Consulting, Inc. was incorporated in 2013 and is headquartered in Kowloon, Hong Kong. ABV Consulting, Inc. is a subsidiary of Kang Min Global Holdings Limited.
